Interface UIActivationListener


  • public interface UIActivationListener
    The observer pattern is used. A class can implement this interface if it will be notified when it should enable or disable certain UI elements.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Group White, I2p, BFH Berne, Contact
